<lb n="0332a13" ed="X"/><lb n="0662a16" ed="R128"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0332a1301">南無此摩揭提國婆<note n="0332a1301" resp="CBETA" type="add">呾【CB】，咀【卍續】</note><app n="0332a1301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">呾</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">咀</rdg></app>那城中得菩薩無依處道場
<lb n="0332a14" ed="X"/><lb n="0662a17" ed="R128"/>解脫門，既自開解，復為人說第四幻智無依善友
<lb n="0332a15" ed="X"/><lb n="0662a18" ed="R128"/>賢勝優婆夷。</item></list>
